pact in constraining the optical potential\nparameters compared to the polarization data. The angular ranges for the\noptimum experimental constraints can vary significantly with the observable\nconsidered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Dec 2020 21:47:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2021 22:40:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
